{
  "stem": "21349.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had, for instance, a president at that time, and they had services.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jews were living there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did any more people come?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Does anyone-- I don't know what they really wanted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just [LAUGHS] wanted-- wanted a connection with the Jewish community to make sure, you see, you have everyone, because they had lists of every block of every house where people were living.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my-- my intention was different than their intention, because my intention was to get people out of concentration camps in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, I had a second kind of objective.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in the beginning, just to get them out of them concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a certain Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Parchman, P-A-R-C-H-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was never brought to trial for what he did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why, and-- But I met him all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went there two or three times a week, and this was a special building which was-- Bremen, and you have to know Bremen was a city, a medieval city, which had a trench around it and a wall.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the trench, and the 'trench' in German is called [GERMAN], [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "W-A-L-L. ?] And [CLEARS THROAT] there was this house, and there was no sign on it what it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nothing there, only a bell up on the top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I pushed the bell, and the door would open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then when the door would open, there was a big stairway upstairs, going upstairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the bottom of the stairway was a big picture of a person like this with two fingers, and the word 'schweigend.' 'Schwiegend' means to be silent.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't talk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then he said to me, come upstairs to room number so and so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
